<sentence id="1">The immediate-early gene egr-1 encodes a transcription factor ( EGR1 ) that links B-cell antigen receptor ( BCR ) signals to downstream activation events through the regulation of previously unidentified target genes .</sentence>
<sentence id="2">Here we identify the gene encoding the lymphocyte homing and migration protein CD44 as a target of EGR1 regulation in B cells .</sentence>
